    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Presenting an investment-grade E46 M3 Coupe, featuring the high-revving S54 3.2L inline-six power plant with individual throttle bodies and an 8,000 RPM redline. This example is mechanically flawless, with the critical VANOS system overhauled and the rear subframe reinforced to prevent common floor-pan fatigue. The Getrag 6-speed manual transmission provides tactile engagement, paired with a perfectly functioning M Variable Differential Lock for optimal torque distribution. The factory Carbon Black paint maintains its original depth and luster, free of imperfections. All bushings, cooling system components, and rod bearings have been addressed, ensuring this chassis performs with the precision of a showroom-fresh unit. A truly turn-key specimen for the serious collector.",
