    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Presenting a truly exceptional, collector-grade vehicle that has been meticulously maintained since day one. This car remains in showroom condition, having been exclusively garage-kept and shielded from the elements. The exterior paint retains its original deep luster, free of any swirls, chips, or imperfections; the ceramic-coated finish ensures a mirror-like shine. Every body panel is perfectly aligned, reflecting a life of careful ownership. Inside, the cabin is indistinguishable from new; the premium leather upholstery remains supple with no bolster wear or creasing, and the original factory floor mats are in pristine condition. All technological features, from the high-fidelity surround sound system to the adaptive climate control, function flawlessly with zero electronic gremlins. Under the hood, the engine bay is spotless, showcasing a complete and documented service history with only OEM parts used. The vehicle drives tight and responsive, with smooth shifts and a quiet cabin. This is a rare opportunity to own a vehicle that feels as though it just rolled off the assembly line. Purchase includes all original keys, the full suite of owner\u2019s manuals, and a comprehensive maintenance log.",
