    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "Offered is a museum-quality 2004 BMW M3 (E46). This example features the high-revving S54 3.2L straight-six, boasting individual throttle bodies and a precision-tuned double-VANOS system. The drivetrain is anchored by a crisp 6-speed Getrag manual gearbox and a factory variable M differential lock. Crucially, the rear subframe has been reinforced and the rod bearings replaced, addressing all chassis and internal longevity concerns. The suspension geometry remains stock for an authentic analog feel, while the paint depth and interior bolsters show zero signs of fatigue. A turn-key investment for the discerning collector seeking peak mechanical harmony.",
